AUXILIARY_DESCRIPTIONS.Ramon Gonzalez Sanchez: Co-conspirator, van driver, and participant in the smuggling operation with Ortega-Chavez and Alejandro Gonzalez Delgado, arrested at the bridge for attempting to smuggle illegal aliens into the United States
AUXILIARY_DESCRIPTIONS.Alejandro Gonzalez Delgado: Co-conspirator and participant in the smuggling operation with Ortega-Chavez and Ramon Gonzalez Sanchez, arrested for being an undocumented alien
AUXILIARY_DESCRIPTIONS.Alfredo Ortega-Chavez: Defendant and appellant convicted of conspiracy to bring or attempt to bring undocumented aliens into the United States, involved in smuggling operation with Ramon Gonzalez Sanchez and Alejandro Gonzalez Delgado, charged with conspiracy and aiding and abetting
